            "title": "Viral networks and detection of potential zoonotic viruses in bats and rodents: A worldwide analysis",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Fabiola",
                    "lastName": "Nieto-Rabiela"
                },
                {
